question: Koh-khoán chè-tō͘, àn-chiàu bān-gô͘ Bí-kim kè-kè ê hāu-ióng, tī 2011 nî 12 goe̍h kah 2012 nî 7 goe̍h tiong-kan chiah ū siōng-tōa ê kò͘-tāi kiam-chiok-chè ê kiam-chiok?
answer: deposits under the retrospective responsibility plan

question: Chik chioh, uī Dec 2011 ê sî-kan, lâi phah-sǹg 'class a common stock ê tùi téng hāng-sò͘ ê kiám-chió' ê chóng kim-chè (bān-gôan tōa-sè) ê kè-chu, iōng hit kok sî-kan ê 'effective price per share' lâi chò.
Tī sūi-liōng 'sò-tiāu piān-choán-lu̍t hō͘-siong chò-choáⁿ chiūⁿ ki̍t-tū khò-lāi kó͘-sū chha-chōe chìn-chhut liáu āu' bē-iú siâⁿ-chòe ê sî-kî, siâⁿ-chòe ê kiâⁿ-kiâⁿ kio̍k chha-pī sī siáⁿ-chē?
Chik-koan ê si-keh chè-kè hām kiat-kò͘ tī 2011 nî 12 goe̍h kah 2012 nî 7 goe̍h ê piàn-tōng chhin-chhiūⁿ án-chóaⁿ?
answer: Tī 2011 nî 12 goe̍h kah 2012 nî 7 goe̍h chi kan, kong-si ê kè-tiâu ài-chiap ū tâng-ka, chhiam-chhiat chòe giâm-kó͘ si-keh ê tâng-ka tùi $101.75 kàu $125.50. Tāi-chāi ê khòng-koan chè-kò͘ khòaⁿ--khí-lâi koh koh hō͘ iân-chek, hām 'si-keh ê chha-bié ê sò͘-liōng kám-chió' tùi 15 pah-bān kàu 1 pah-bān ê chha-bié, kah Class B huat-seng chha-chhé ê hām 'thang siá-chò Class B chū-téng si-keh' ê tâng-ka lóng ū chió-chió ê kám-chió.

question: Tī 7-ge̍h 2012 nî ê sî-chūn, hō͘-sǹg kap 12-ge̍h 2011 nî pí, ū hā-tiāu ê hāng-bo̍k chi-tiong, ūi-chiáⁿ chi̍t ê sī ēng sió-siòng sò͘ chò piau-chún, m̄-sī siá chò pah bān kó͘ goh bān kó͘ îⁿ?
answer: conversion rate of class b common stock to class a common stock after deposits

question: Tùi December 2011 kàu July 2012, 'effective price per share' ê phah-un-tè thè kí-tiâu chē-chió?
Tsiah-nà "tui-tāi siu-tí-tāi chek-jīm kè-uē hā-ê chioh-chú" tī 2012 nî 7 goe̍h ê chioh-chú, kā 2011 nî 12 goe̍h ê sò͘-jī kiám-chí 50%, hit-ê sin ê chioh-chú tiāu chē-chē (bān gûn)?
Jī-ê sî-kan thîng-chán lâi kóng, "sî-keng kà-siàu muí-ê hòe" kah "hō͘-thn̂g āu ê tùi-tâng chi-phòe ê tōa-siàu bōe thò" chi-kan ū sím-mih bē-tàng-tit ê koan-hē?
answer: Chit-ê chu-liāu sī-chāi ún-tāi ū chi̍t ê tùi-tâng-sèng ê koan-hē. Tī 2011 nî 12 goe̍h kah 2012 nî 7 goe̍h chi-kan, tong "sî-keng kà-siàu muí-ê hòe" tùi $101.75 tōa kàu $125.50, "hō͘-thn̂g āu ê tùi-tâng chi-phòe ê tōa-siàu bōe thò" tùi 104 pah-bān ê chi̍t-ê kiam-sè kàu 103 pah-bān. Che piáu-bīn chi-phòe, tong chi-phòe ke-thiⁿ kiâⁿ-chòe koh-khah ū kè-tiâu, chi-phòe ê tōa-siàu bōe thò ê sò͘-liōng iā chián-chián kiám-sè.

question: Tī chia ê piáu lāi ū kúi ê sò͘-kì sī kāng "class a common stock" ū tī-ê liân-hē?
Tùi nn̄g ê kî-kan lâi khuàⁿ, siáⁿ êMetrics ū Tōa-ê kái-piàn tōa-sè-liōng, pí lén i ê chha-pia̍t kap kúi-tāi Metrics ê chha-pia̍t lâi kàu-tōe?
answer: ‘Deposit under the retrospective responsibility plan’ sī siáⁿ-mih ê Tōa-ê Chha-pia̍t. I ê kòe-chióng tōa-liōng kiám-chió liáu $1415 million ($1565M - $150M), siáⁿ-mih ê chha-pia̍t koh-khah tōa-ê kòe-chióng piàn-tōa koh-khah tōa-ê kúi-tāi Metrics. Tùi tōa-liōng kóng, siáⁿ-mih ê share price piàn-tōa liáu chí $23.75 kap siáⁿ-mih ê share piàn-tōa liáu siōng-chē 14 million, hō͘ deposit ê piàn-tōa tōa-liōng koh-khah tōa-ê uī-tōaⁿ.

question: 2 ê kî-kan, Class A thong-siông kó͘ ê tùi-tâng hō͘-sò͘ ê cheng-chē sī siáⁿ-mih?
